Using Abstract Refinements
--------------------------

<div class="mybreak"><br></div>

**Inference FTW!**

<div class="mybreak"><br></div>

\begin{code}
{-@ insertSort :: (Ord a) => [a] -> Incrs a @-}
insertSort xs = foldr insert [] xs

insert x []     = [x]
insert x (y:ys)
  | x < y       = x : y : ys
  | otherwise   = y : insert x ys
\end{code}

